rity of their value in  and  these companies have heavy debt loads that simply couldn’t be maintained with the oil price slide dozens of master limited partnerships have declined in value in  and  the  billion masterlimitedpartnership sector is the sausage maker of the investment world buyers love the yields — now averaging about  — but many know little about how the yields are generated the bullish pitch by brokers in favor of the investments centered around the highyielding way to participate in the booming us energy infrastructure buildout unfortunately the investments while providing generous yields masked the substantial high risks of these investments many of these investments were pitched to elderly and conservative investors because of the relatively high dividends and yields that the investments paid out these losses are potentially recoverable through either finra arbitration claims against the brokerage firms whose brokers recommended the investments or lawsuits against the promoters of the investments fraud based claims the second type of oil and gas actions deal with fraud based claims oil and gas investments take many forms including limited partnership interests master limited partnerships ownership of fractional undivided interests in leases and general partnerships risk level tax consequences and investor liability vary according to the type of program drilling partnerships have always been a gamble but unfortunately many oil and gas scams have been perpetrated by bad actors in the securities industry although some of the con artists moved on to more lucrative venues since the oil boom ended in the mids many continued to linger on in the oil field and the results of their actions are being felt now fraudulent oil and gas deals are frequently structured with the limited partnership or other legal entity in one state the operation and physical presence of the field in a second state and the offerings made to prospective investors in states other than the initial two states thus there is less chance of an investor dropping by a well site or a nonexistent company headquarters such a structure also makes it difficult for law enforcement officials and victims to identify and expose the fraud our securities law firm holds financial advisors accountable brokers at major brokerage firms like linsco lpl ubs merrill lynch raymond james citgroup and stifel nicolaus also sometimes engage in an activity called “selling away” when a broker sells a customer an “investment” outside the investment products offered by the brokerage firm and outside the client’s account there may be a selling away issue these investments known as private securities often involve investments in oil and gas related limited partnerships privately held companies private placements promissory notes and other similar investments sometimes they are real investments other times they are completely bogus and used as a means for the advisor to convert client funds unfortunately unscrupulous oil promoters and stockbrokers frequently use the internet and “boiler room” offices with banks of phones manned by salespeople with little or no background in energy exploration but plenty of experience in highpressure sales their techniques include repeated unsolicited phone calls to potential investors hyping the profitability of the deal and promises of safe but secure returns some examples of these pitches include • you will have an interest in a well that cannot miss • the risks are minimal • a geologist has given the salesperson a tip • the broker or salesperson has personally invested in the venture • the promoter has “hit” on every well drilled so far • there has been a tremendous “discovery” in an adjacent field • a large reputable oil company like chevron is operating or planning to operate in the area • only a few interests remain to be sold and you should immediately send in your money in order to assure the purchase of an interest • this is a special private deal open only to a lucky chosen few investors oil gas and energy deals we are investigating cushing royalty and income fund linn energy llc    parker drilling company  offshore group investment limited  midstates petroleum companytesoro petroleum co tso williams cos wmb kinder morgan kmi eog resources eog spectra energy corp se baker hughes inc bhi newfield exploration co nfx anadarko petroleum corp apc cimarex energy xec marathon petroleum mpc valero energy vlo schlumberger ltd slb conocophillips cop consol energy inc cnx exxon mobil corp xom national oilwell varco inc nov devon energy corp dvn phillips  psx chevron corp cvx eqt corporation eqt oneok oke occidental petroleum oxy fmc technologies inc fti hess corporation hes cameron international corp cam first solar inc fslr marathon oil corp mro helmerich  payne hp halliburton co hal cabot oil  gas cog southwestern energy swn murphy oil mur pioneer natural resources pxd apache corporation apa noble energy inc nbl chesapeake energy chk qep resources qep nabors industries ltd nbr diamond offshore drilling do range resources corp rrc ensco plc esv noble corp ne denbury resources inc dnr transocean rig if you lost money in oil gas or energy related investments please call our chicago based investment fraud law firm for a free evaluation by a lawyer as to whether those losses can be recovered through the finra arbitration process or through a lawsuit at  recent posts please call  today if you suffered forcefield energy fnrg losses and were recommended the investment by gerald cocuzzo and newbridge securities oil and gas recommendations with stephen swarbrick how to sue questar capital corp oil and gas investment losses because of joe zenker and raymond james losses with emerald oil how we can help for investors with noble royalty access funds berry petroleum company llc  bakersfield ca   skip to content search   berry petroleum company llc berry petroleum company llc linkedin home about berry operations corp responsibilitycommunity investors contact legal notice our story continues… explore recent news company profile berry petroleum is an independent privatelyheld energy company engaged in the acquisition exploration development and production of domestic oil and natural gas reserves primarily located in the san joaquin basin in california the uinta basin in utah the piceance basin in colorado the hugoton basin in kansas and the east texas basin in texas our focus the company’s focus is on the responsible and safe exploration and development of oil and natural gas   berry emphasizes the prudent maintenance of its existing assets by leveraging the application of technological innovation and knowledge base of its employees the focus for the asset teams is to meet operational objectives while maintaining a safe working environment and recognizing the company’s responsibility to its surrounding communities our history berry petroleum’s roots reach back to  through its predecessor companies founded by cj berry those ties are still evident from the operating areas assets and even people that bridge the time and evolution of the first berry entities to the current berry petroleum read more go to top berry petroleum  bakersfield ca foursquarelog insign upnearbyget inspiredtop pickstrendingfoodcoffeenightlifefunshoppingberry petroleumofficebakersfieldsavesharetipsphotos berry petroleumno tips and reviewslog in to leave a tip herepostno tips yetwrite a short note about what you liked what to order or other helpful advice for visitors photosrelated searchesberry petroleum bakersfield  berry petroleum bakersfield photos  berry petroleum bakersfield location  berry petroleum bakersfield address  berry petroleum bakersfield  berry petroleum bakersfield  aboutblogbusinessescitiesdevelopershelpjobscookies updatedprivacy updatedtermsenglishenglish français deutsch bahasa indonesia italiano  한국어 português русский español ภาษาไทย türkçe citiesatlantaaustinbostonchicagodallasdenverhouston